name: inspirational and memorable Calendar 2012 - by riasnelli
description:
With the new year approaching, I am excited to represent a new B/W Calendar. This Calendar called “inspirational and memorable” is a deep insight into my inspirational people and memorable dates in 2012 . Each page represent a person or date with respective month.

You can buy this soft copy as PDF format and print on fine matte paper 200 g/m & consists of 13 pages and cover. 

Once i got payment confirmation from Paypal i will sent you the High Quality PDF format for Printing.

you can also check the entire pages from below link:
